name: VP-BDT
description:
VP-BDT is Vertikal Horizon a project that is trying to change my habit of taking pictures/photograph. Usually I just look, then take pictures of objects that are only available in front of me and at one point I feel quite bored with it. To overcome my boredom, then try to see objects that are above or below my camera and take pictures. Yes, the vertical horizon project as simple as that, but the results I've got were beyond my expectations.
